    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small song bird native to the Canary Islands, the Azores, and Madeira. Wild birds are yellow-green with brownish streaking on the back. The species in captivity exists in a several color varieties, most commonly yellow.</Note_Text>
